.TH "FIXTURE-ADMIN" "1" "2026-06-04" "cargo-orthohelp 0.8.0" "Fixture Manual"
.SH NAME
fixture-admin \- Administers fixture state.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B fixture-admin
[\fB\-\-scope\fR \fISCOPE\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Administers fixture state.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-scope\fR \fISCOPE\fR
Scope to administer.
.br
Default: \fBlocal\fR
.SH ENVIRONMENT
.TP
\fBNESTED_APP_SCOPE\fR
Scope to administer. Equivalent to \fB\--scope\fR.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
\fB0\fR
Successful execution.
.TP
\fB1\fR
General errors.
.SH COMMANDS
.SS audit
Audits fixture state.
.PP
OPTIONS:
.TP
\fB\-\-dry-run\fR
Reports intended audit actions.
.SS grant-access
Grants access to a principal.
.PP
OPTIONS:
.TP
\fB\-\-principal\fR \fIPRINCIPAL\fR
Principal receiving access.
